data.description: NEW FLOORING AND QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS COMING SOON! Updates will be installed on 01/25/2024. New Bathroom vanities, new floors in main areas (kitchen/dining, living room, hall and spare bath) New quartz counter tops and cabinets updated as well! Charming 3BR, 2BA with a Bonus room. This inviting residence features a cozy living room with wood burning fireplace perfect for comfortable living. Enjoy a bonus room that adds versatility to your space. Newer stainless steel appliances in kitchen. The property features a private back yard with a newer fence. Roof replaced 2 years ago. Brand new HVAC. Conveniently located in Berwick Lakes community. NO HOA. Close to I-16, shopping and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
